      'Afore Consulting AS was instrumental to executing the almost impossible deadlines of the IT separation of Statoil Fuel & Retail ASA from Statoil ASA',
  },
  {
    name: 'Trond Ellefsen, CIO office Statoil ASA',
    content:
      'When executing the Statoil Hydro merger Afore Consulting saved us tens of millions by exceptional project execution - and we delivered on time!',
  },
